# Simulate a OTP Verification System / Password / Bank ATM Pin

-> The user will be asked to enter an 4 Digit OTP 

-> The User will be given 3 Max Attempts to enter correct OTP 

-> Assume the Correct OTP is already Stored 

-> Aks the user to input 4 Digit OTP 

-> If the OTP is not 4 Digit number display 

    -> OTP Must be 4 Digit NUmber Only 

-> If the OTP is 4 Digit number and also correct OTP 

    -> Correct OTP - SUCCESS 

-> If the OTP is incorrect, decrease the Attempts Count 

-> After 3 Attempts display

    -> Maximum Attempts Reached, Try After 24 Hours 